    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my awesome car! It\u2019s been incredibly well-loved and is in really solid, reliable shape. It drives like a dream and has plenty of life left in it for all your road trips. It\u2019s super clean inside and out, and I\u2019ve always made sure to keep it running smoothly. It's been such a dependable ride for me, and I know you're going to love how it handles. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
