      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six engine with VarioCam Plus. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response and linear power delivery through a precise 6-speed G96 manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS) to ensure long-term reliability. The suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup for superior lateral grip. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over ventilated rotors, showing excellent bite with no fading. While the exterior displays the honest patina of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the chassis remains stiff and the hydraulic steering rack provides the communicative feedback synonymous with the 996.2 platform. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
